<h1>Your Fitness Profile</h1>
<div class="result">
  <label>Age:</label>
  <span><%= @user.age %></span>
</div>
<div class="result">
  <label>Height (cm):</label>
  <span><%= @user.height %></span>
</div>
<div class="result">
  <label>Weight (kg):</label>
  <span><%= @user.weight %></span>
</div>
<div class="result">
  <label>BMR:</label>
  <span><%= @bmr %></span>
</div>
<div class="result">
  <label>TDEE:</label>
  <span><%= @tdee %></span>
</div>

<div class="feedback">
  <p>Based on your details, these are your daily macronutrient requirements. Keep up the good work and stay active!</p>
</div>
